gachaInformation.summary:
Introducing the Release Celebration Gacha!

This Gacha includes only 2★ or higher characters!
Pull from the 10x Gacha to get a guaranteed 3★ or higher character!
4★ characters that are pulled for the first time come with a Costume.
Getting a Costume unlocks the option in the Costume Shop to make the same one or color variants of it for other characters.

Receive 1 Release Celebration Gacha Sticker for every character obtained from the Release Celebration Gacha.
Exchange 300 Release Celebration Gacha Stickers for one of the characters listed in the Release Celebration Gacha Sticker Exchange.
gachaInformation.description:
•Once Daily Gacha can only be pulled using Paid Crystals.
•A valid COLORFUL+ can be used to pull from the Once Daily Gacha up to twice a day.
•Once Daily Gacha resets at 4:00AM PST daily.
•When pulling from this Gacha, Free Crystals will be used first where applicable.
•Characters from this Gacha will be in a pre-Upgraded state.
•Duplicate characters may be pulled from this Gacha.
•Duplicate characters are automatically sent to the Green Room.
•Gacha characters are pulled one at a time based on existing drop rates. The drop rates therefore do not mean that, for example, characters with a drop rate of 1% are guaranteed to appear once every 100 pulls.
•When pulling from the 10x gacha, if no 3★ or higher characters are pulled, the tenth slot will be pulled again using guaranteed slot drop rates.
•Drop rates can be viewed from the drop rates tab.
•Stats and skills of new characters can be viewed by tapping the Character Details button on the Gacha screen.
•After starting the Gacha, even if the app should force-quit or be disconnected without displaying the Gacha results screen, pulled characters will be saved and viewable either on the Characters screen or in the Green Room.
•Release Celebration Gacha Stickers are valid for exchange until January 16, 2022 at 2:59PM PST. After this period, they will be converted into an equivalent number of Wish Pieces.
•The Gacha schedule is subject to change without notice.

•A valid COLORFUL+ can be used to pull from the Once Daily Gacha up to twice a day.
•Once Daily Gacha resets at 4:00AM PDT daily.
•When pulling from this Gacha, Free Crystals will be used first where applicable.
•Characters from this Gacha will be in a pre-Upgraded state.
•Duplicate characters may be pulled from this Gacha.
•Duplicate characters are automatically sent to the Green Room.
•Gacha characters are pulled one at a time based on existing drop rates. The drop rates therefore do not mean that, for example, characters with a drop rate of 1% are guaranteed to appear once every 100 pulls.
•When pulling from the 10x gacha, if no 3★ or higher characters are pulled, the tenth slot will be pulled again using guaranteed slot drop rates.
•Drop rates can be viewed from the drop rates tab.
•Stats and skills of new characters can be viewed by tapping the Character Details button on the Gacha screen.
•Characters that come with Costumes can be confirmed from the drop rates tab.
•After starting the Gacha, even if the app should force-quit or be disconnected without displaying the Gacha results screen, pulled characters will be saved and viewable either on the Characters screen or in the Green Room.
•Romantic Bride Gacha Stickers are valid for exchange until July 18, 2022 at 2:59PM PDT. After this period, they will be converted into an equivalent number of Wish Pieces.
•New Limited Time Characters in this Gacha will no longer appear once this Gacha ends, but may be made available again in the future. Any potential future availability is currently TBD.
•New non-Limited Time characters in this Gacha will also appear in future Gacha, but their drop rates may differ.
•The Gacha schedule is subject to change without notice.

gachaInformation.summary:
Introducing the (1 Time Only) Romantic Bride Gacha!

This Gacha can only be pulled once per player using Paid Crystals.

Including Limited Time Characters, this Gacha features 3 new characters with higher drop rates than other characters of the same rarity.
Pull from the 10x Gacha to get a guaranteed 3★ or higher character!

New Characters

- Limited Time Characters
4★ "A Love Song Dedicated To You" Toya Aoyagi
4★ "Fantastic Planner" Rui Kamishiro
- Normal
4★ "Sparkling Curiosity☆" Kagamine Len 

Some 4★ characters that are pulled for the first time come with a Costume or a Hairstyle.
Getting a Costume unlocks the option in the Costume Shop to make it for other characters that can wear it.
Costumes made for other characters may come with slightly different patterns or accessories.
Hairstyles that come with characters can be obtained by reaching Mastery Rank 2.
These hairstyles cannot be used with other characters.
To view Costume details, go to Characters > Costumes.

Receive 1 Romantic Bride Gacha Sticker for every character obtained from the (1 Time Only) Romantic Bride Gacha.
Exchange 300 Romantic Bride Gacha Stickers for one of the characters listed in the Romantic Bride Gacha Sticker Exchange.
You can also exchange 10 Romantic Bride Gacha Stickers for 1 Limited Gacha Sticker Voucher in the Romantic Bride Gacha Sticker Exchange.

■Gacha Bonuses
For every Pull from the Rainbow Harmony Gacha, Bonuses will be acquired.
The amount of Gacha Bonuses you can acquire will differ depending on the type of Crystals you spend for each Pull.

-Free Crystals: +0.5
-Paid Crystals: +1
*Spending both Free Crystals and Paid Crystals in the Pull 1x Gacha: +0.5

Once you have acquired 50 Gacha Bonuses, you will get one 4★ character guaranteed.
Once you have acquired 100 Gacha Bonuses, you will get one of the following new 4★ characters guaranteed: 4★ "The Feelings We've Realized" Saki Tenma, 4★ "A Tomboyish Melody" Kagamine Rin, 4★ "Lunchtime Chat" Shiho Hinomori.

*The drop rates for 4★ characters when you have acquired 50 Gacha Bonuses and the drop rates for 4★ featured characters when you have acquired 100 Gacha Bonuses are equal.
*Gacha Bonuses cannot be used outside of their own Gacha.
*Gacha Bonuses acquired from their own Gacha, cannot be carried over to future Gacha.

Furthermore, up to 10 Limited Gacha Sticker Vouchers can be used to exchange for one of the characters listed in the JP 1.5 Year Anniversary Colorful Festival Gacha Sticker Exchange or Yearning for Spring, A Moment in the Night Gacha Sticker Exchange.
gachaInformation.description:
•Once Daily Gacha and 1 Time Only Gacha can only be pulled using Paid Crystals.
•Once Daily Gacha resets at 4:00AM PDT daily.
•Gacha Bonuses are not applicable in this Gacha.
•A valid COLORFUL+ can be used to pull from the Once Daily Gacha up to twice a day.
•You can also use a Gacha Ticket to pull from Gacha that are normally pulled with Free Crystals.
•Gacha Tickets will be used first over Free Crystals.
•When pulling from this Gacha, Free Crystals will be used first where applicable.
•Characters from this Gacha will be in a pre-Upgraded state.
•Duplicate characters may be pulled from this Gacha.
•Duplicate characters are automatically sent to the Green Room.
•Gacha characters are pulled one at a time based on existing drop rates. The drop rates therefore do not mean that, for example, characters with a drop rate of 1% are guaranteed to appear once every 100 pulls.
•When pulling from the 10x gacha, if no 3★ or higher characters are pulled, the tenth slot will be pulled again using guaranteed slot drop rates.
•Drop rates can be viewed from the drop rates tab.
•Stats and skills of new characters can be viewed by tapping the Character Details button on the Gacha screen.
•Characters that come with Costumes can be confirmed from the drop rates tab on the Gacha Details screen.
•After starting the Gacha, even if the app should force-quit or be disconnected without displaying the Gacha results screen, pulled characters will be saved and viewable either on the Characters screen or in the Green Room.
•JP 1.5 Year Anniversary Gacha Stickers are valid for exchange until May 11, 2023 at 2:59PM PDT. After this period, they will be converted into an equivalent number of Wish Pieces.
•New Limited Time Characters in this Gacha will no longer appear once this Gacha ends, but may be made available again in the future. Any potential future availability is currently TBD.
•The Gacha schedule is subject to change without notice.

Introducing the [It's Back] Colorful Festival Gacha!

In the [It's Back] Colorful Festival Gacha, the drop rate of 4★ rarity characters is doubled to 6%.
Includes two Colorful Festival Limited characters.
In addition, you can also pull from the 1 Time Only 10x Gacha for 1,500 Paid Crystals.
This Colorful Festival Gacha reissue will be exactly the same as before.

Colorful Festival Limited Characters
4★ "Someday, I'll Deliver" Haruka Kiritani
4★ "To You Who Wants To Be An Idol" Airi Momoi

Some 4★ characters that are pulled for the first time come with a Costume or a Hairstyle.

You can also exchange 10 [It's Back] Colorful Festival Gacha Stickers for 1 Limited Gacha Sticker Voucher in the [It's Back] Colorful Festival Gacha Sticker Exchange.
